fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.store.javamail

Class JMStoreFolder

  • Object
    • fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.core.StoreFolder
      • fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.store.javamail.JMStoreFolder

  • public class JMStoreFolder
extends StoreFolder
    StoreFolder sub-class for mail boxes extracted through JavaMail library.

    For now, IMAP and Thunderbird mbox, eml structure through MailExtract application, could also be used for POP3 and Gmail, via StoreExtractor (not tested).
